article_id:1393,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Maintenance Notice for 6/23(PT)  [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592982000"></span>]</strong></span><br>The maintenance has been completed on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592982000"></span>.</div><div><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send three exquisite honey and three blessed ethon ashes to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592971200"></span>.<br><br>These gifts can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592976600"></span>]</strong></span><br>Please be aware that the maintenance has been extended.<br>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.</div><div><br></div><div>Maintenance is scheduled to end on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592982000"></span>.<br>Thank you for your patience.</div><hr><div>We will be performing server maintenance during the following period. You will not be able to obtain rewards if you complete a quest during the maintenance period. Please also claim any 30-Day Pack (Recovery) rewards before maintenance begins.</div><div><br></div><div>â– Maintenance Period</div><div>Around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592971200"></span> to around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592978400"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You will not be able to play Dragalia Lost during the maintenance.</div><div>2. Maintenance may start and/or end before or after the scheduled times.</div><div><br></div><div><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1592373600,update_time1592982028